text: @RepMattGaetz Florida had record #COVID19 deaths today. Over 100 died. Shameful. It was preventable for most. Do you regret mocking the virus and masks in congress months ago? I know, it's not a GOP priority, not like TikTok, statues and Obama. FL deserves better. #VoteBlueToSaveAmerica2020
